com.team1285.frc2016.subsystems

Class Drivetrain

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.command.Subsystem
      • com.team1285.frc2016.subsystems.Drivetrain
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.NamedSendable, edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.Sendable

    public class Drivetrain
extends edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.command.Subsystem
    The subsystem that is used for the drive train of the robot. It runs the 4 motors in the drive train as well as read the encoder values from the motors.
    Since:
    2016-10-16
    Author:
    Kaveesha Siribaddana
